{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act14side", "eventName": "風雪過境", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BI-7", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "破冰", "storyInfo": "在博士的幫助下，阿克托斯重整態勢，菈塔托絲則將指揮權交給了妹妹。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g3_mainhall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268", "name2": "avg_npc_268"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sjoyasorrow_intro", "key": "$sjoyasorrow_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268", "name2": "avg_npc_268", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉！", "name": "長老A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268", "name2": "avg_npc_268", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣？", "name": "長老B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268", "name2": "avg_npc_268", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些“山雪鬼”果然不讓我們離開。", "name": "長老A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說什麼恩希歐迪斯說為了我們的安全著想，要我們待在這裡，不要隨意走動。", "name": "長老A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268", "name2": "avg_npc_268", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看，我就說，他恩希歐迪斯就是要將我們關在這裡！", "name": "長老B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268", "name2": "avg_npc_268", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今大長老昏迷不醒，聖女又沒有戴冠，他嘴上說著另外兩家是叛徒，我看他也沒安好心。", "name": "長老A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268", "name2": "avg_npc_268", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓......唉，現在說這些又有什麼用呢，院內的事務一向由大長老決斷，如今大長老這副樣子，我們也不知道該怎麼辦啊。", "name": "長老B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道說事情變成這副樣子也是耶拉岡德的旨意嗎......", "name": "長老C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德是否想要如今的境況不好說，但是祂若看到你們這副樣子，想必會感到痛心。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268", "name2": "avg_npc_268", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖、聖女大人！", "name": "長老A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268", "name2": "avg_npc_268", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們......我們只是在擔憂......", "name": "長老B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼值得擔心的事？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大長老的情況......還有如今三大家族的狀況......", "name": "長老C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才我問過醫生，大長老的情況確實不容樂觀，但他掌管蔓珠院這麼多年，想必耶拉岡德也會保佑他。我相信，大長老一定會好起來的。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這期間，院內無論大小事項一切由我代為決斷。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268", "name2": "avg_npc_268", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......", "name": "長老A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人本就要在戴冠儀式上成為這謝拉格的管理者，大長老也早有讓聖女大人接班的意思，現在情況特殊，有何不可？", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#5$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說，各位長老有更好的主意？", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#5$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268", "name2": "avg_npc_268", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一個侍女長......", "name": "長老A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268", "name2": "avg_npc_268", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "罷了，雅兒侍女長說得確實不錯。", "name": "長老B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們本就信服聖女大人的能力，現在聖女大人願意站出來穩定人心，自然沒有比這更好的事。", "name": "長老B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，各位長老也不必憂心。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大典上發生那樣的事，恩希歐迪斯確實有這麼做的理由。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而即便恩希歐迪斯真的不懷好意，有我在，蔓珠院也不會有事。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若是聖獵中的聖女，其存在只讓人覺得耀眼奪目。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今的聖女，卻讓人覺得有一股氣勢，一股無法違抗的氣勢。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長老們面面相覷，然後紛紛低下頭。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“全憑聖女大人安排。”"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都下去吧。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268", "name2": "avg_npc_268", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅，剛才很威風哦。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#7$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的，我還以為你從大典回來後，會很失望呢。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在看來，是我多心了。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我確實很失望。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，上一次失望的時候，我什麼都說不出口。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時的我，沒有辦法為自己爭取任何東西。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而這一次，我雖然很失望，但我知道，我已經擁有能夠改變一些東西的力量了。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，這一次，我不希望我只能失望了，我應該去做一些事情，讓我自己不再失望。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......恩雅，你真是長大了。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果可以的話，我希望我永遠是個孩子，整天去思考這些東西太麻煩了......", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你說得對，我長大了。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g5_guestroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信仰......", "name": "大長老"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......咳咳。", "name": "大長老"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大長老，您終於醒了！", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#3$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要喧嘩。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#3$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大典......咳咳，怎麼樣了？老朽......只記得，審問布朗陶家的人的事了，在那之後，就記不得了。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您被阿克托斯老爺下毒，然後，諾希斯的出現讓局勢更加複雜了。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，阿克托斯老爺與菈塔托絲夫人聯手想要制伏恩希歐迪斯老爺，卻被恩希歐迪斯老爺反過來壓制......", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老朽要聽的不是這個。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴冠儀式呢？聖女呢？還政呢？", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......儀式被中止了，恩希歐迪斯老爺宣佈，在收服佩爾羅契家和布朗陶家後，重新舉辦儀式。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......恩希歐迪斯，咳咳。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女呢？", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人......此時正在自己的房間裡。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小傢伙，第一次旁聽三族議會的感覺如何？"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......大長老爺爺，我沒想到，三族議會竟然是這麼無聊的事情。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三位家主只說著和自己家族有關的事，在提到每年行事由哪家出力時也都興趣缺缺，他們根本不關心耶拉岡德。"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵，聰明的孩子，老朽果然沒有看錯你。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......大長老爺爺，您是故意讓我看到這些的嗎？"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不錯。"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為總有一天，你會成為大長老。"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，你會明白，所謂的信仰，究竟意味著什麼。"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......在蔓珠院多久了？", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？二十五年，大長老。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這二十五年，咳咳，你可覺得，這蔓珠院，這謝拉格有什麼變化？", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......除了希瓦艾什家帶來的一些東西，我覺得沒有什麼變化。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這片土地，千年以來都沒有什麼變化。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#3$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "未來，也不應當有所變化。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#3$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，扶老朽起來。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是大長老，您的身體......", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老朽的身體，咳咳，老朽自己知道。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老朽已經時日無多。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去請聖女到正殿，就說，老朽有話和她說。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g8_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，這是我第二次被你救了。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自從恩希歐迪斯返回謝拉格，建立他的喀蘭貿易以來，我就一直看不慣他的做法。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#9$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您在進入謝拉格的時候恐怕也已經看到了，他建的貿易港，我已經看不懂了。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#9$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他帶進來的那些東西，我用過，確實好用，我手下也有些人在用，我知道。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "底下那些年輕人以為我不知道他們在聊什麼，我怎麼會不知道。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但恩希歐迪斯這麼搞不行，他這樣只會把謝拉格往火坑裡推。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德在上面看著，這麼搞，謝拉格會遭報應的。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我一直帶頭反對他，但是，結果卻是現在這樣。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我佩爾羅契家上下都不是喜歡玩那些花花腸子的人。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原本還有一個瓦萊絲，可我現在......", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以信任你嗎？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#6$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_252", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，菈塔托絲來了。", "name": "Sharp"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_252"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#6$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿克托斯？我以為你已經急不可待地發動所有你能發動的兵力去和恩希歐迪斯打起來了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#6$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不是博士阻攔，我怎麼可能忍得住。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島的博士......", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你救了我一命，照理說，我應當回報你。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，如果你想要的是我背後的布朗陶家，那我只能對你說一聲抱歉了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你的幫助必不可少。;（幫她理一理大衣的領子）;別把人想得這麼壞。", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line221", "option2": "line221", "option3": "line221"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line228"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這倒是我這幾天以來聽到的最順耳的一句話了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#6$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "3"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你和我非親非故，而你又做出了這麼大的事，告訴我，我要怎樣才能不想多？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然阿克托斯在這裡，我不用想都知道你們想要什麼。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不怕告訴你，在你的手下找到我之前，我已經認真考慮過要向恩希歐迪斯投降了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你確定我能幫上你什麼？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "如果阿克托斯也願意投降，那確實不用了。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我佩爾羅契家，絕不可能投降。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......所以呢，你們打算怎麼做？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "首先，你們已經輸了。;首先，我並不能幫你們取得勝利。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用你強調我也知道。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "民心現在站在了恩希歐迪斯那邊，他在大典結束後，甚至只宣佈我和阿克托斯的“罪行”而沒有對我們兩家的領地有進一步動作。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#6$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他看來，謝拉格已經是他的囊中之物了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#6$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而實際上也確實是這樣。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，以你的智慧看，還有什麼可做的事情？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "那麼，眼下最明智的破局點，是去營救聖女。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在這個局面，確實也只有聖女站出來才有回轉的可能。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯控制蔓珠院就是為了不讓聖女有說話的餘地。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問題是——恩希歐迪斯不會猜不到你會這麼做。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒不如說，他派兵去看住蔓珠院，不就是等著你去自投羅網嗎？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "正面突破當然不行。;需要做幾手準備。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g12_mountpath", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_198_blackd_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "營救聖女？", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯沒有立刻去攻打另外兩家有兩個原因。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一是他覺得沒有必要。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二是他擔心那個博士會出手協助佩爾羅契家。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_198_blackd_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士......如果博士真的協助阿克托斯的話，那很多事就不好說了。", "name": "魏斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_198_blackd_1#6$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，這個博士並不是真的要操控阿克托斯的軍隊來和我們分庭抗禮。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照你們的說法，他想要制止阿克托斯莽撞地發動全面戰爭，以此來減少流血衝突的可能性更大。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不十分相信這個可能性，在我看來，他想要操控佩爾羅契家和布朗陶家，借此一躍成為謝拉格另一個霸主的可能性並不低。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_198_blackd_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_199_yak_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士不是這樣的人。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#2$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_198_blackd_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_199_yak_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，雖然他可能真的具有這樣的能力。", "name": "魏斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_198_blackd_1#2$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......無論是你們，還是恩希歐迪斯，對這個人的評價，有點讓我感到不可思議。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望你們的判斷沒有出錯。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，無論是哪種可能性，他們都是最有可能衝著如今被我們控制的聖山來的。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想要扭轉輿論上的局勢，聖女的發言必不可少。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果他們真的能夠把聖女從聖山帶出去，那恩希歐迪斯就可以說是功虧一簣了。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個道理，那個博士不會不懂。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以他一定會來。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_198_blackd_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_199_yak_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......真是諷刺，在他們看來，我們希瓦艾什家，居然成為了挾持自己大小姐的人。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#10$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道不是嗎？恩雅·希瓦艾什，現在是我們的人質。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_198_blackd_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你不喜歡這種說法，我可以換一種，聖女成為了我們重要的籌碼。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#5$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不會改變任何東西。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#5$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_198_blackd_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......諾希斯，能請你別再刺激角峰了嗎？", "name": "魏斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_198_blackd_1#9$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在幫你們認清現實。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說，你們其實不知道，恩希歐迪斯最終要做的，絕不是什麼還政。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將這個國家交給宗教，從一開始就不在他的計畫內。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_198_blackd_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不是在說，恩雅·希瓦艾什有什麼不好。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對她沒有興趣，自然也沒有什麼意見。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她成為了聖女，並且她做得很好。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那她就必然會成為恩希歐迪斯的阻礙，僅此而已。事已至此，不允許舞台上存在做得比希瓦艾什家家主更好的人。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_198_blackd_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_199_yak_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我知道。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#10$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然知道。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#10$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不是在玩一局可以重來的遊戲，不要給自己增加不必要的麻煩。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫希，偵查就交給你了。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g8_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，這個計畫好！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#10$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你確定？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "當然。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "表面急行軍實施破壞，看起來是為了營救尤卡坦，並且吸引對方注意，讓對方對你的目的產生誤解。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你讓正面大部隊負責落實這種誤解。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實際這一切都是為了讓阿克托斯的隊伍能夠接近聖山，並且山上還會有你的手下提前滲透進去接應......", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然遠遠算不上穩妥，但確實好像行得通。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐧呢，就算你能對付恩希歐迪斯那支打扮成山雪鬼的隊伍，這個真正的怪物不解決，就永遠別想說對付得了恩希歐迪斯。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "Sharp。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_252"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是工作的一部分？", "name": "Sharp"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_252"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_252"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "是的。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說得這麼輕鬆，你真的有把握嗎？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_252"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道，但我應該能拖住她十幾分鐘吧。", "name": "Sharp"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_252"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你也是個怪物。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......所以，羅德島的博士，你就這麼篤定我會幫你？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我不會強迫你。;這套計畫中，沒有你一定要參與的環節。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這個人，有些地方和恩希歐迪斯倒是挺像的。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#6$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你把你的計畫這麼輕易地告訴了我，還和我說不會強迫我。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我已經知道了每一個環節。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有人會放這樣的人離開。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了......", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我替你去。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲，別鬧了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你先照照鏡子看看你現在的樣子再說這話吧，菈塔托絲。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "疲憊，蒼白，雙眼無神。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怎麼可能放心讓你以這副樣子去救我的丈夫？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且我不知道你在那間屋子裡和恩希歐迪斯說了什麼。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我可不想看著布朗陶家就這麼被你交到恩希歐迪斯手上！", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#8$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#6$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞪我幹嘛，想吵架嗎？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一次，你倒是沒錯。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，羅德島的博士，休露絲會代表我協助你的計畫。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實際上，我依然對於能夠從恩希歐迪斯手上拿回點什麼不抱期望。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只能說，祝你好運。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "tr